class Solution {
    public boolean squareIsWhite(String coordinates) {
        int columns=coordinates.charAt(0)-'a'+1;
        int row=coordinates.charAt(1)-'0';
        if((row+columns)%2==0){
            return false;
        }
        return true;
    }
}

Note: Convert alphabet to number:
a → 1
b → 2
c → 3
Formula:
column = s.charAt(0) - 'a' + 1
Convert row character to number
row = s.charAt(1) - '0'
